Symbol.Script_3D:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
! ============================================================================= ! GS Window Opening Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Window Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, gs_IsCurved = 0, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
UnID = 1 hotspot a/2, 0, 0, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1 hotspot a/2, ac_wallhole_height, 0, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1 hotspot -a/2, 0, 0, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1 hotspot -a/2, ac_wallhole_height, 0, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1
hotspot a/2, 0, -WALL_THICKNESS, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1 hotspot a/2, ac_wallhole_height, -WALL_THICKNESS, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1 hotspot -a/2, 0, -WALL_THICKNESS, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1 hotspot -a/2, ac_wallhole_height, -WALL_THICKNESS, UnID : UnID = UnID + 1
! ============================================================================= ! Preview in Object Settings Dialog ! =============================================================================
pen WALL_VIEW_PEN
if GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 1 | GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 3 | GLOB_FEEDBACK_MODE then for i=22.5 to 337.5 step 45 put A/2/cos(22.5)*cos(i), A/2/cos(22.5)*sin(i), 15 next i
cprism_ WALL_MAT_A, WALL_MAT_B, WALL_MAT_EDGE, 7+nsp/3,WALL_THICKNESS, A/2+0.2, -B/2-0.2, 8, A/2+0.2, B+0.2-B/2, 8, -A/2-0.2, B+0.2-B/2, 8, -A/2-0.2, -0.2-B/2, 8, A/2+0.2, -B/2-0.2, -1, A/2, 0, 13, get(nsp), A/2, 0, -1 end endif
if GLOB_PREVIEW_MODE = 2 then for i=22.5 to 337.5 step 45 put A/2/cos(22.5)*cos(i), A/2/cos(22.5)*sin(i), 0 next i
addy A/2 extrude 2+nsp/3, 0, 0, WALL_THICKNESS, 16+32, A/2, 0, 0, get(nsp), A/2, 0, -1 del 1 end endif

Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: iTypeCurvedWallCut CUT_PARALLEL = 1 CUT_RADIAL = 2
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
if GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 7 | GLOB_SCRIPT_TYPE = 8 then goto "MasterEnd" ! forward migration, backward migration
! ============================================================================= ! Main Definitions ! =============================================================================
EPS = 0.0001
iWindowShape = 6 ! SHAPE_OCTAGONAL bParalellInCurvedWalls = (iTypeCurvedWallCut = CUT_PARALLEL)
"MasterEnd":
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Contact person: <SzL, NJ>
values "A" range(0, ) values{2} "iTypeCurvedWallCut" CUT_PARALLEL, `Параллельно`, CUT_RADIAL, `Радиально` values "gs_frame_thk" range[0,]
if gs_pen_2D <= 0 then parameters gs_pen_2D = 3
! Wall Contour Left/Right --------------------------------------------------------------
gs_stack_right = not(gs_stack_right_contour) parameters gs_stack_right = not(gs_stack_right_contour)
gs_stack_left = not(gs_stack_left_contour) parameters gs_stack_left = not(gs_stack_left_contour)
B = A parameters B = B
! ============================================================================= ! GS Window Opening Functions ! =============================================================================
call "GS Window Opening Functions", parameters all iWindowShape = iWindowShape, bParalellInCurvedWalls = bParalellInCurvedWalls
! ============================================================================= ! Orientation ! =============================================================================
ac_OpeningSide = "" parameters ac_OpeningSide = ac_OpeningSide
! ============================================================================= ! IFC Parameters ! =============================================================================
ifc_optype = 10 ! WIN_OP_USER_DEFINED parameters ifc_optype = ifc_optype call "IFC_optype_window" parameters ifc_optype = ifc_optype
lock "ifc_optypestr"
!**************** Swedish list parameter control ********************** if gs_SWE_listParams_contr > 0 then call "SWE_ListParameters_control" parameters gs_SWE_listParams_contr = gs_SWE_listParams_contr, swe_list_f1 = swe_list_f1 endif
